dcterms:description: Natural Questions (NQ) is a dataset for passage retrieval, containing natural language questions as data points and passages from Wikipedia as targets. It includes over 21 million targets and approximately 60K training examples.

dcterms:description: MSMARCO is a dataset containing natural language questions and passages extracted from web documents, designed for machine reading comprehension. It includes 8.8 million targets and 500K training examples.
